metadata.description:
For centuries, a diverse breed of Pepe-dogs has lived happily on the fertile lands inherited from the Great-Classic-Pepe's. But their time has passed, and the time has come when the Great-Classic-Pepe-Titans decided to wake up from their eternal sleep and return everything to the Classics and lay the foundation of a new era

The age of the Pepe-dogs is over, but they are still grateful to the Classic-Pepe's for a great time
